Sentencas: A simple, fast, and economical alcohol penetration method for assessing the solid oxide cell to metal window frame seal in a typical planar design is presented.
Titulo: Leak test for solid oxide fuel cells and solid oxide electrolysis cells

Sentencas: An alcohol such as ethanol or isopropanol is placed into the cavity of a cell sealed to the window frame.
Titulo: Leak test for solid oxide fuel cells and solid oxide electrolysis cells

Sentencas: Within 3-5 min, one can determine if the glass seal is hermetic by visual observation along the seal edges on the side of the sealed frame.
Titulo: Leak test for solid oxide fuel cells and solid oxide electrolysis cells

Sentencas: Cross bubbling and open circuit voltage methods for determining whether the seal failed or cracked at high temperature after final stack firing are also discussed.
Titulo: Leak test for solid oxide fuel cells and solid oxide electrolysis cells
